<HL>
   R.H. Macy Sells
   Small Equity Stake
   To New York Firm
   ----
   By Jeffrey A. Trachtenberg
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
08/03/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C9
</SO>
<CO>
   MZ
</CO>
<IN>
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
